---

---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-number">01.</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I graduated with a degree in <strong>Computer Engineering</strong> from the
          <strong>University of Indonesia</strong> (Class of 2018). Blending a strong
          foundation in hardware-software integration with modern software engineering,
          I specialize in bridging the gap between core backend systems and cutting-edge
          Artificial Intelligence.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans designing intelligent AI agents, building infrastructure automation
          tools, and architecting end-to-end systems for production AI workloads.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight">
          <span class="highlight-label">Education</span>
          <span class="highlight-value">B.Eng Computer Engineering</span>
          <span class="highlight-sub">Universitas Indonesia, 2018</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight">
          <span class="highlight-label">Focus</span>
          <span class="highlight-value">AI Agents & Infrastructure</span>
          <span class="highlight-sub">Backend systems + AI integration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .highlight {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .highlight-value {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .highlight-sub {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
</style>
